---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Read" description="Weekly essays on meaning, worldview, and living with intention.">

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-20">

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-medium mb-4">Read</h1>
    <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Weekly essays exploring meaning, worldview, faith, and what it takes to live coherently.
      Published on Substack - free to subscribe, free to read.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-10">
      <p>
        Each essay starts with a question worth asking and follows it wherever it leads -
        through philosophy, theology, psychology, current events, and everyday life. The
        goal isn't to tell you what to think. It's to give you better tools for doing it yourself.
      </p>
      <p>
        Expect the voice to be warm but direct. Intellectually serious but never academic.
        A little playful where it helps. And always, always honest.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://humanonpurposeproject.substack.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-block bg-accent text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-sm font-medium hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors text-center"
      >
        Subscribe on Substack
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://humanonpurposeproject.substack.com/archive"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-block border border-accent text-accent px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-sm font-medium hover:bg-accent-light/50 transition-colors text-center"
      >
        Browse the archive
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>

</BaseLayout>
